<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure L 27. Labels. i Bulimus hondurasanus Pfeiffer, 1846 ii Bulimus huascensis Reeve, 1848 iii Bulimus humboldtii Reeve, 1849 iv Helix hygrohylaea d'Orbigny, 1835 v Otostomus emeus hypozonus Martens, 1893 vi Bulimus ignavus Reeve, 1849." , "Figure 8. Bostryx species. A Bostryx affinis (Broderip in Broderip and Sowerby I 1832), possible syntype NHMUK 20100610 (H = 27.5) B Bostryx huascensis (Reeve, 1848), lectotype NHMUK 1975159 (H = 19.1) C Bostryx mejillonensis (Pfeiffer, 1857), lectotype NHMUK 1975322 (H = 24.1) D Bostryx kathiae Breure, 1978, paratype NHMUK 1975228 (H = 17.5) E Bostryx obliquistriatus (da Costa, 1901), lectotype NHMUK 1907.11.21.41 (H = 28.9) E Bostryx rhololarynx papillatus (Morelet, 1860), syntype NHMUK 1893.2.4.192 (H = 22.7) G Bostryx rhololarynx rhodolarynx (Reeve, 1849), lectotype NHMUK 1975434 (H = 34.5). All enlarged." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26792" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26625" .

